## What Needs to Change (all in `src/pipelines.js`)

**5 surgical edits, no existing code touched:**

### 1. Add import (lines 20–45)
Add `AutoModelForImageTextToText` to the existing `import { ... } from './models.js'` block — it's already exported from `src/models.js` (line 8736), just not imported in `pipelines.js`.

### 2. Add typedefs (after `DocumentQuestionAnsweringPipeline` ~line 2779)
Three JSDoc typedefs following the exact same pattern as `ImageToTextPipeline`/`DocumentQuestionAnsweringPipeline`:
- `ImageTextToTextSingle` — `{ generated_text: string }`
- `ImageTextToTextOutput` — array of single
