- `ImageTextToTextPipelineType` — intersection type for the class

### 3. Add the class (right after the typedef block)
```js
export class ImageTextToTextPipeline extends Pipeline {
  async _call(image, text, generate_kwargs = {}) {
    const preparedImage = (await prepareImages(image))[0];
    const image_inputs = await this.processor(preparedImage);
    const text_inputs = this.tokenizer(Array.isArray(text) ? text : [text], { padding: true, truncation: true });
